music-industry-cheat-codes-she-gave-chappell-roan-and-doechii-for-handling-fame-3833042">凯蒂·佩里（Katy Perry）的邮政音乐行业“作弊代码”，她给了查佩尔·罗恩（Chappell Roan）和杜希（Doechii）处理名望，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Katy-Perry-Chappel-Roan-and-Doechii.-Credit-Lisa-Lake-Steven-Simione-and-Michael-Loccisano-via-GETTY.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Katy Perry，Chappel Roan和Doechii。图片来源：丽莎湖，史蒂文·西奥恩（Steven Simione）和迈克尔·洛奇萨诺（Michael Loccisano）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Katy-Perry-Chappel-Roan-and-Doechii.-Credit-Lisa-Lake-Steven-Simione-and-Michael-Loccisano-via-GETTY.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Katy-Perry-Chappel-Roan-and-Doechii.-Credit-Lisa-Lake-Steven-Simione-and-Michael-Loccisano-via-GETTY-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Katy-Perry-Chappel-Roan-and-Doechii.-Credit-Lisa-Lake-Steven-Simione-and-Michael-Loccisano-via-GETTY-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Katy-Perry-Chappel-Roan-and-Doechii.-Credit-Lisa-Lake-Steven-Simione-and-Michael-Loccisano-via-GETTY-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Katy-Perry-Chappel-Roan-and-Doechii.-Credit-Lisa-Lake-Steven-Simione-and-Michael-Loccisano-via-GETTY-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Katy-Perry-Chappel-Roan-and-Doechii.-Credit-Lisa-Lake-Steven-Simione-and-Michael-Loccisano-via-GETTY-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/Katy-Perry">凯蒂·佩里（Katy Perry）</a>对她的提示和“作弊代码”开放，她在处理名望时给了<a href="/artists/Chappell-Roan">Chappell Roan</a>和<a href="/artists/Doechii">Doechii</a> 。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/katy-perry-every-single-ranked-3776044">凯蒂·佩里（Katy Perry）：按照伟大顺序排名</a></strong></li></ul><p>在对<a href="https:/