" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/chappell_mexico_lucha.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/chappell_mexico_lucha-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/chappell_mexico_lucha-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/chappell_mexico_lucha-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/chappell_mexico_lucha-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/chappell_mexico_lucha-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3825404" class="wp-caption-text"> Chappell Roan于2024年8月1日在伊利诺伊州芝加哥的Grant Park举行的Lollapalooza音乐节举行。 （图片由Erika Goldring/Wireimage）</figcaption></figure><p>佩里还告诉该出版物：“我不得不去寻找所有这些工具并治愈一些自己的东西。”</p><p>在其他新闻中，佩里将于1月30日与<a href="/artists/Billie-Eilish">Billie Eilish</a> ， <a href="/artists/Stevie-Nicks">Stevie Nicks</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/joni-mitchell">Joni Mitchell</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/red-hot-chili-peppers">Red Hot Chili Peppers</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sting">Sting</a> ，Sting， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/stevie-nicks">Stevie Nicks，Gracie Abrams</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gracie-abrams">Gracie Abrams，</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/green-day">Green Day</a> ，Green Day等人一起<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/stevie-wonder-the-black-crowes-anderson-paak-and-more-complete-fireaid-benefit-concert-line-up-3830921">在即将举行</a>的Fireeid Beady Face Concert演出。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/katy-perry-shares-music-industry-cheat-codes-she-gave-chappell-roan-and-doechii-for-handling-fame-3833042">凯蒂·佩里（Katy Perry）的邮政音乐行业“作弊代码”，她给了查佩尔·罗恩（Chappell Roan）和杜希（Doechii）处理名望，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
