l release the album on April 4 via Lucky Number / Polyvinyl and you can pre-order/pre-save it <a href="https://momma-band.ffm.to/welcome-to-my-blue-sky" target="_blank" rel="noopener">here</a> . It will be the band&#39;s fourth album in total and serves as the follow-up to 2022&#39;s &#39;Household Name&#39;.</p><p> &#39;I Want You (Fever)&#39; showcases the band&#39;s spiky, &#39;90s-throwback indie aesthetic, with hooky, double-vocal leads and scuzzy, slacker guitar lines. Watch the Jaxon Whittington-directed video below. </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="妈妈 - 我想要你（发烧）（音乐视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/WG0mAzP165o?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> Speaking about the song, the band have said: “&#39;I Want You (Fever)&#39; is a song we wrote about wanting to be with someone who has a girlfriend, or someone who isn&#39;t over their ex. It&#39;s pining after someone, but there&#39;s also some confidence knowing that that person wants to be with you. The second we wrote that song we felt like we were entering a new era – we scrapped everything we had written for the album up to that point because it felt so fresh and so exciting.” </p><figure id="attachment_3833037" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3833037" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3833037" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Momma-Welcome-To-My-Blue-Sky-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="Momma 'Welcome To My Blue Sky' album artwork. Credit: PRESS" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Momma-Welcome-To-My-Blue-Sky-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Momma-Welcome-To-My-Blue-Sky-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Momma-Welcome-To-My-Blue-Sky-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Momma-Welcome-To-My-Blue-Sky-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Momma-Welcome-To-My-Blue-Sky-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Momma-Welcome-To-My-Blue-Sky-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Momma-Welcome-To-My-Blue-Sky-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3833037" class="wp-caption-text"> Momma &#39;Welcome To My Blue Sky&#39; album artwork. Credit: PRESS</figcaption></figure><h2> <strong>&#39;Welcome To My Blue Sky&#39; tracklist:</strong> </h2><ol><li data-leveltext="%1)" data-font="" data-listid="865" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335551671&quot;:1,&quot;335552541&quot;:0,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769242&quot;:[65533,0,46],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;%1)&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"> <strong>&#39;真挚地&#39;</strong> </li><li data-leveltext="%1)" data-font="" data-listid="865" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335551671&quot;:1,&quot;335552541&quot;:0,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769242&quot;:[65533,0,46],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;%1)&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"> <strong>&#39;I Want You (Fever)&#39;</strong> </li><li data-leveltext="%1)" data-font="" data-listid="865" data-li